title: OIP 22: Policy Framework
body:
### Summary
Adopt a framework distinguishing: 
- (1) key policy decisions that require a community vote
- (2) technical levers that the policy team uses to implement community decisions, in which case the policy team should act with autonomy

The framework doesn't introduce anything new, but rather formalizes the current Policy boundaries and decision-making process.

![](https://i.imgur.com/lW7sNrm.png)

![](https://i.imgur.com/vKCBBbS.png)

Additional context, explanation and discussion of this proposal can be found on the forum:

https://forum.olympusdao.finance/d/92-oip-22-approve-policy-framework
### Vote
**For:** Adopt Policy framework
**Against:** Don't adopt Policy framework
